How do you hadle the merge conflict?
A merge conflict occurs when Git can not automatically merge changes from different branches.

How do you hadle the merge conflict?
When a merge conflict occurs first i identify cinficted the file using command "git status". Then i open the
files, review the conflicting changes and decide which code to keep or how to combine both changes. After resolving
the conflicts, i stage the files using "git add" and verify the status and complete the merge with "git commit" or
"git merge" Finally i test the application to ensure the merged code works correctly.
